        "product_description": {
            "value": "The GEAR AID Revivex Wash and DWR Care Kit includes everything you need to keep high-tech GORE-TEX gear looking good and performing like new. This kit features 10 fl oz of Revivex Pro Cleaner, a concentrated tech wash that effectively removes dirt, grime and stains without stripping off your gear's durable water repellent (DWR) coating. The Pro Cleaner restores breathability and cleans up to 20 jackets or 10 sleeping bags, and works on GORE-TEX fabric, eVent, NeoShell, Omni-Tech and more waterproof breathable materials. The kit also includes 10.5 oz of Revivex Durable Water Repellent, a high-performance, breathable and washable spray that adds or restores water repellency on jackets, waders, gloves and other insulated and non-insulated outerwear. Use this easy care system to clean, restore breathability, and protect your outerwear from water, dirt and stains. Keep your gear in tip-top shape with the GEAR AID Revivex Wash and DWR Care Kit.",
            "is_required": true,
            "source": "ai",
